00:20:29,225 --> 00:20:30,350
Arashi.

289
00:20:30,725 --> 00:20:32,375
The race went off without a hitch!

290
00:20:32,825 --> 00:20:34,168
Even though those guys were

291
00:20:34,184 --> 00:20:35,606
caught during the competition.

292
00:20:36,525 --> 00:20:37,875
As for the situation,

293
00:20:38,300 --> 00:20:41,525
the organizer will handle it later.

294
00:20:41,700 --> 00:20:42,975
From now on...

295
00:20:43,250 --> 00:20:44,250
Thanks.

296
00:20:44,832 --> 00:20:47,525
- You were worried, huh?
- Not at all.

297
00:20:48,300 --> 00:20:50,028
I knew if anyone could handle it,

298
00:20:50,053 --> 00:20:51,295
it'd be you, Arashi.

299
00:21:09,425 --> 00:21:10,725
In the past...

300
00:21:12,720 --> 00:21:15,450
I used to date that person.

301
00:21:19,725 --> 00:21:21,475
He was kind to me at first.

302
00:21:23,500 --> 00:21:25,600
But then, he suddenly started to hit me.

303
00:21:31,100 --> 00:21:32,615
It became more and

304
00:21:32,640 --> 00:21:33,999
more intense day by day,

305
00:21:36,775 --> 00:21:38,250
and it left scars.

306
00:21:41,050 --> 00:21:42,471
Even though my friends

307
00:21:42,480 --> 00:21:44,160
told me to leave him.

308
00:21:46,025 --> 00:21:48,825
But I didn't listen to them.

309
00:21:51,425 --> 00:21:53,075
I thought it was because I was bad

310
00:21:54,850 --> 00:21:57,125
and I thought he loved me.

311
00:22:01,175 --> 00:22:02,300
One day,

312
00:22:04,250 --> 00:22:05,925
I was tied to the bed.

313
00:22:08,000 --> 00:22:09,400
Took off my clothes,

314
00:22:12,400 --> 00:22:14,500
he brought his friends,

315
00:22:22,325 --> 00:22:23,675
and they raped me.

316
00:22:31,475 --> 00:22:32,900
After he laughed

317
00:22:33,900 --> 00:22:35,200
and played,

318
00:22:36,975 --> 00:22:38,175
he said he got tired of me

319
00:22:39,525 --> 00:22:40,775
and threw me away.

320
00:22:53,500 --> 00:22:56,000
Why are you crying?

321
00:22:59,125 --> 00:23:00,475
Because Kai doesn't cry.

322
00:23:01,875 --> 00:23:04,250
If Kai can't cry, I'll cry for him.

323
00:23:08,450 --> 00:23:10,675
If Kai suffers, I suffer with him.

324
00:23:11,850 --> 00:23:13,029
If Kai is in pain,

325
00:23:13,053 --> 00:23:14,264
I'll endure the pain too.

326
00:23:17,075 --> 00:23:18,225
Therefore...

327
00:23:20,750 --> 00:23:22,550
Don't carry it alone anymore.

328
00:23:28,675 --> 00:23:32,000
You're allowed to cry when it hurts.

329
00:23:35,800 --> 00:23:37,225
I'm here for you.

330
00:23:40,150 --> 00:23:41,550
I will wipe your tears

331
00:23:42,575 --> 00:23:43,775
and take care of you.

332
00:23:47,825 --> 00:23:48,825
So,

333
00:23:51,875 --> 00:23:53,025
cry,

334
00:23:53,800 --> 00:23:54,720
Kai.

335
00:24:17,700 --> 00:24:18,900
Fuma-san.

336
00:24:20,375 --> 00:24:21,850
Can I...

337
00:24:24,975 --> 00:24:26,750
love you?

338
00:24:27,250 --> 00:24:28,825
Don't ask me that.

339
00:24:30,100 --> 00:24:31,625
My greatest wish

340
00:24:33,825 --> 00:24:35,450
is for Kai to love me.

341
00:24:43,825 --> 00:24:45,020
I'm sorry.

342
00:24:47,125 --> 00:24:48,550
If we had met sooner,

343
00:24:51,667 --> 00:24:53,253
I would have been able to protect Kai

344
00:24:53,600 --> 00:24:55,325
before anything happened.

345
00:24:59,550 --> 00:25:00,700
But...

346
00:25:02,450 --> 00:25:03,675
we met now.

347
00:25:18,325 --> 00:25:19,525
These tears...

348
00:25:21,000 --> 00:25:22,975
they're happy tears.

349
00:25:26,150 --> 00:25:27,325
Thank you

350
00:25:29,025 --> 00:25:31,150
for saving me

351
00:25:32,600 --> 00:25:33,875
from my nightmare.

352
00:25:36,925 --> 00:25:38,190
It should be me

353
00:25:38,214 --> 00:25:39,753
thanking you for telling me.

354
00:25:42,575 --> 00:25:43,875
I'm happy too.

355
00:25:46,820 --> 00:25:48,351
I'll show you by my actions

356
00:25:48,376 --> 00:25:50,359
from now on, not promises.

357
00:25:53,425 --> 00:25:55,046
I will make Kai so happy

358
00:25:55,070 --> 00:25:56,570
that everyone will envy him.

359
00:26:00,350 --> 00:26:03,750
I'm afraid of more happiness.

360
00:26:08,800 --> 00:26:10,503
Then, I will make you so happy

361
00:26:10,519 --> 00:26:12,199
that you forget the fear.

362
00:26:14,650 --> 00:26:16,375
I will make Kai smile all the time.

363
00:26:20,975 --> 00:26:22,300
Me too.

364
00:26:28,075 --> 00:26:29,075
Again.

365
00:26:30,200 --> 00:26:31,425
No, no.

366
00:26:31,625 --> 00:26:32,975
- Again.
- Hey.

367
00:26:33,825 --> 00:26:34,900
Mm.

368
00:26:38,475 --> 00:26:39,475
No.

369
00:27:00,475 --> 00:27:01,700
Does it sting?

370
00:27:04,225 --> 00:27:05,450
I'm fine.

371
00:27:09,225 --> 00:27:11,900
When you tried to help me,

372
00:27:13,775 --> 00:27:15,775
I fell in love with you again.

373
00:27:17,500 --> 00:27:18,571
Have you ever fallen

374
00:27:18,580 --> 00:27:19,790
