375
00:27:29,725 --> 00:27:31,750
Can't you hear my heart?

376
00:27:34,150 --> 00:27:36,525
If you don't tell me, I won't know.

377
00:27:44,400 --> 00:27:46,175
I love Rei.

378
00:27:54,825 --> 00:27:57,175
Me too.

379
00:27:59,325 --> 00:28:01,000
What's the same?

380
00:28:03,350 --> 00:28:05,000
Don't cheat.

381
00:28:14,025 --> 00:28:17,875
Rei loves Arashi.

382
00:28:23,000 --> 00:28:24,125
The weather.

